ture has never been discovered. It waits latently to take its place in intellectual history.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aAufklärung. 4aLiteraturtheorie. 4aRhetorik. 4aÄsthetik. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aEnlightenment.  aLiterary theory.  aaesthetics.  arhetoric.1 aMahler, Anthony.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2020z978311069628808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter English eBooks 2020 - UCz978311065906108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020 Englishz978311070474708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020z9783110704532oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97831106234820 cprintz978311062331440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110624519zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110624519zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110624519.jpg  a978-3-11-065906-1 De Gruyter English eBooks 2020 - UCb2020  a978-3-11-069627-1 DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-069628-8 DG Ebook Package English 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070474-7 EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020 Englishb2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2020